1.  TACHYONE FOR STYLING PURPOSE.
	
it is same as bootstrap. Give more and shorter class for styling.
	ex: grow for shaking image in little larger.
	shadow-4 for shadowing, pa3, ma3 for padding and margin 
	  
	TO INSTALl: npm install tachyons
	To use :  import 'tachyons';


2. API FOR fetching avatar image based on name.

 <img src={`https://joeschmoe.io/api/v1/${props.name}`} alt="Avatar" />

 3. Google fonts apply in css page

 @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Gugi&display=swap');

AND apply  :    font-family: 'Gugi', cursive;